{
  "meta": {
    "id": "dreadheim_meadhall",
    "title": "Dreadheim • Mead Hall",
    "bg": "/guildbook/scenes/dreadheim_meadhall.png",
    "portrait": "/guildbook/npcs/hel/frame_008.png",
    "speakerDefault": "Hel",

    "keys": {
      "nameKey": "va_player_name",
      "goodKey": "va_good",
      "evilKey": "va_evil",
      "bowKey": "va_bowedToHel",
      "flagsKey": "va_flags",
      "questIdKey": "vaq_activeQuestId",
      "questCatKey": "vaq_activeQuestCatalog"
    },

    "goodKickThreshold": 10,
    "kickedOutByLokiJson": "/data/episodes/volume1_ep1/kickedoutbyloki.json"
  },

  "start": "hel_1",

  "nodes": [
    {
      "id": "hel_1",
      "speaker": "Hel",
      "text": "So, you’re the one Loki dragged in from the frost. Tell me—do you not bow when you enter the presence of Hel herself, or has the cold stolen even that much sense?",
      "choices": [
        { "label": "Bow before Hel.", "to": "hel_bow" },
        { "label": "I bow to no one.", "to": "hel_no_bow" },
        { "label": "Is Hel supposed to be important to me?", "to": "hel_important" }
      ]
    },

    {
      "id": "hel_bow",
      "speaker": "Hel",
      "text": "Good. A rare instinct—respect. Stand. And remember: mercy is not the same thing as warmth.",
      "reward": {
        "set": { "va_bowedToHel": true },
        "good": 1,
        "flags": { "metHel": true, "bowedToHel": true, "dq_001_bow_complete": true }
      },
      "choices": [
        { "label": "Continue.", "to": "hel_2" }
      ]
    },

    {
      "id": "hel_no_bow",
      "speaker": "Hel",
      "text": "Mm. Proud. Or foolish. In Dreadheim, the difference is measured in scars.",
      "reward": {
        "set": { "va_bowedToHel": false },
        "evil": 1,
        "flags": { "metHel": true, "bowedToHel": false }
      },
      "choices": [
        { "label": "Continue.", "to": "hel_2" },
        { "label": "Try again…", "to": "hel_1" }
      ]
    },

    {
      "id": "hel_important",
      "speaker": "Hel",
      "text": "I am the silence beneath laughter. The daughter of endings. And tonight, I watch you.",
      "reward": {
        "flags": { "metHel": true }
      },
      "choices": [
        { "label": "Bow before Hel.", "to": "hel_bow" },
        { "label": "I bow to no one.", "to": "hel_no_bow" },
        { "label": "Why are you watching me?", "to": "hel_watch" }
      ]
    },

    {
      "id": "hel_watch",
      "speaker": "Hel",
      "text": "Because Loki doesn’t drag in strays unless they bite back. Prove you’re not a pet.",
      "choices": [
        { "label": "Give me a task.", "to": "hel_quest" },
        { "label": "I answer to no one.", "to": "hel_proud" }
      ]
    },

    {
      "id": "hel_proud",
      "speaker": "Hel",
      "text": "Good. Keep that. But don’t confuse pride with power.",
      "reward": {
        "flags": { "helPride": true }
      },
      "choices": [
        { "label": "I need work. A quest.", "to": "hel_quest" },
        { "label": "Continue.", "to": "hel_2" }
      ]
    },

    {
      "id": "hel_2",
      "speaker": "Hel",
      "text": "Do not mistake warmth for mercy, {name}. In Dreadheim, even the hearth has teeth.",
      "choices": [
        { "label": "I need work. A quest.", "to": "hel_quest" },
        { "label": "Say nothing.", "to": "hel_3" }
      ]
    },

    {
      "id": "hel_quest",
      "speaker": "Hel",
      "text": "If you want a mark in this hall—take something small, and take it clean. Then return to me.",
      "reward": {
        "setQuest": {
          "id": "dq_001",
          "catalog": "/guildbook/quests/dreadheim_quests.json"
        },
        "flags": { "dq_001_started": true }
      },
      "choices": [
        { "label": "I’ll do it.", "to": "hel_3" },
        { "label": "What if I refuse?", "to": "hel_refuse" }
      ]
    },

    {
      "id": "hel_refuse",
      "speaker": "Hel",
      "text": "Then you stay unmarked. And in Dreadheim, the unmarked are easy to erase.",
      "choices": [
        { "label": "Fine. I’ll do it.", "to": "hel_3" },
        { "label": "Leave the hall.", "to": "hel_end_leave" }
      ]
    },

    {
      "id": "hel_3",
      "speaker": "Hel",
      "text": "Keep your voice low. Watch the benches. The ones who smile first are usually hungry.",
      "choices": [
        { "label": "Who’s hungry for me?", "to": "hel_hungry" },
        { "label": "Continue.", "to": "hel_4" }
      ]
    },

    {
      "id": "hel_hungry",
      "speaker": "Hel",
      "text": "Everyone. Some want your gold. Some want your fear. A few want your name in their mouth.",
      "reward": {
        "flags": { "warnedByHel": true }
      },
      "choices": [
        { "label": "Continue.", "to": "hel_4" }
      ]
    },

    {
      "id": "hel_4",
      "speaker": "Hel",
      "text": "If you’re here, you’ve already chosen survival over innocence. Good.",
      "choices": [
        { "label": "I chose survival.", "to": "hel_survival" },
        { "label": "I chose power.", "to": "hel_power" }
      ]
    },

    {
      "id": "hel_survival",
      "speaker": "Hel",
      "text": "Then you’ll learn faster than most. Survive long enough and the hall will bow back.",
      "reward": {
        "coins": 10,
        "items": [{ "id": "sigil_fragment", "name": "Sigil Fragment", "qty": 1 }],
        "flags": { "path": "survival" }
      },
      "choices": [
        { "label": "Continue.", "to": "hel_5" }
      ]
    },

    {
      "id": "hel_power",
      "speaker": "Hel",
      "text": "Power takes payment. If you want it, bleed for it—quietly.",
      "reward": {
        "coins": 10,
        "items": [{ "id": "ashen_token", "name": "Ashen Token", "qty": 1 }],
        "flags": { "path": "power" }
      },
      "choices": [
        { "label": "Continue.", "to": "hel_5" }
      ]
    },

    {
      "id": "hel_5",
      "speaker": "Hel",
      "text": "Now go. Dreadheim is waiting to see what you become.",
      "choices": [
        { "label": "Close", "to": "__close" }
      ]
    },

    {
      "id": "hel_end_leave",
      "speaker": "Hel",
      "text": "Run, then. The frost always remembers names.",
      "choices": [
        { "label": "Close", "to": "__close" }
      ]
    }
  ]
}


